query:
/*+  */ select count(*)
from question AS q
inner join tag_question AS tq
on tq.question_id = q.id AND q.score >= 10 AND q.score <= 1000
inner join site AS s
on tq.site_id = s.site_id AND q.site_id = s.site_id AND s.site_name IN ('stackoverflow')
inner join tag AS t
on tq.tag_id = t.id AND t.site_id = s.site_id AND t.name IN ('angular',
'function',
'git',
'json',
'list',
'qt',
'sql-server',
'sqlite',
'symfony',
'testing',
'ubuntu',
'visual-studio-2010',
'wpf');
